"""
Premier League Prediction League — "Tipovačka"
A score-guessing game for ~10 friends, backed by a Google Sheet.

Scoring:
  Exact score .............. 3 pts   (2-1 vs 2-1)
  Same goal difference ..... 2 pts   (2-1 vs 1-0)
  Right winner only ........ 1 pt    (2-1 vs 3-1)
  Wrong outcome ............ 0 pts

Rounds lock at the first kickoff of the round. Everyone's picks and points
are hidden until then; revealed once locked.

Phase 1 (integrity) notes — see handoff.md for the full contract:
  * Player codes are canonicalised to str(code).strip().upper() on every write
    and every comparison; historical mixed-case rows keep working.
  * Predictions distinguish "no prediction" (None) from an entered 0.
  * Saving re-reads fixtures/players/predictions fresh and re-validates the
    deadline, completeness and žolík allowance server-side before writing.
  * Fixtures and players are validated before any player-facing use; invalid
    rows are excluded (never destructively rewritten) and surfaced to the
    organiser with sheet row numbers.
"""

